The Fanmon Archive This is where information on all of your fan made Digimon are put, from their images, to their stages, to their attributes, everything about them! Moderators: DDC, Razanak7
Fanmon Planning This is where you go to post images and information on your Fanmon you plan on buying. You don't have to have enough cash to post it. Moderators: DDC, Razanak7, Damnationsedge
The Information & Help Board This is where all guides and information are put. You may also post any questions you may have. Moderators: DDC, Kingmana, DarkCat
Suggestions Here you can suggest things for DDC. Moderators: DDC, Kingmana, DarkCat

New User Application Board All new users must create a post with their application to join DDC here! You MUST post here and receive your information before you can play. Once you receive your information, you will be able to post. Moderators: DDC, Kingmana, DarkCat
